doc: This file holds the data for the unit tests and is resource to
`test_fluxes.py`. It is separated into low and high energy data (that
is compared against different energy arrays). For each flux, there is
at least one set of data called `none`, and further datasets for
alternative knee models if they exist for the particular flux.
